divs: Sighting DetailsI was out in front of my house helping my dad out side.I look up at the sky and see a jet trail and a jet then i look over to the left of the jet in front of it there was the UFO a what looked like cyledrical object and had a bright lights on the side i told my dad to look up and he noticed the object also. When i first noticed the object i noticed right away it did not look like any military aircraft but shortley after that i saw another jet flying in the same object and then i saw to more jets and i saw a low flying plane that had 1 big propeld engies on each side of the plane flying in the opposite direction. When i saw the object dissapere it looked like it just vannished i didnt see it anymore.
